2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong:
MLML 263:Appl Comp Ocean-  Lecture, discussion, and technical programming with MATLAB for computation and visualization with applications in marine sciences. Use of existing program libraries for data I/O and analysis. Semester project required. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures. (Offered fall semester.)

(Prereq: Exclude Freshmen and Sophomore and Junior)
